<p>
	This beautiful looking candle is green in colour with white hearts on the surfaces. Its herbal scent cleanses the atmosphere with aromas of pine needle, green leaf and lemongrass, with a subtle hint of nutmeg. Refreshing fragrances of rosemary and thyme blend with deeper notes of patchouli. This candle is also blended with quality geranium and rose essential oils. The candle burns for approximately 35 hours. When in use place the candle tin on a heat resistant surface. Ensure the candle is kept away from any flammable materials and do not move the candle while alight or while the wax is molten. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Do not leave a burning candle unattended. This candle is suitable for vegans.</p>
